{"tid":2081683,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"米高積遜猝逝　不死的傳奇","createTime":"2020-06-27T12:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T11:12:55.000Z","uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf3f0a21ab073db55c9d4ec83cdbc6ef7b6eed26","tid":2081683,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"舞台王者駕崩了。TheKingofPop米高積遜未及復出，便告永別。他前天在家中綵排時心臟病發，搶救無效，結束半世紀的傳奇人生。豹隱多時的MJ，今年3月才宣佈復出，計劃今年7月在倫敦連開50場演唱會，全球萬千歌迷的熱切期待，最終化為懷念與哀悼。<br />\n<br />\n懷念他渾身是勁的超凡舞藝，舞出狂熱境界；懷念他beatit、beatit的反覆歌聲，唱出驚世成就。這位黑人歌手60年代開始揚名，80年代走紅。1982年，《Thriller》大碟一出，結合電影式MV裏耳目一新的勁舞，即時打動舉世流行曲擁躉。<br />\n哀悼他越漂越白的膚色，哀悼他越描越黑的人生。90年代起，MJ醜聞不斷，他被指控孌童，官司纏繞多年。他債台高築，一度欠下39億港元巨款。終年五十，舞台王者活得未免有點急促&hellip;<br />\nButyouarenotalone.<br />\nForIamherewithyou.<br />\nThoughwe'refarapart.<br />\nYou'realwaysinmyheart.<br />\nMJ傳奇，永遠不死。"},{"pid":"257771c5b41a578788eaff2a4965de08507edd94","tid":2081683,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"又死？"},{"pid":"7535bbcde19f2c7c4ca27a1d3ef6555345dda667","tid":2081683,"uid":205043,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"郭窮城有冇得同mj一戰？"},{"pid":"99cdb49d3d06b02de7dcf879577679e2fe0bb22d","tid":2081683,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"257771c5b41a578788eaff2a4965de08507edd94","tid":2081683,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:03:05.000Z","msg":"又死？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"當年今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d26540da47fd842d371cc0ca68a3d4671fc3138","tid":2081683,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7535bbcde19f2c7c4ca27a1d3ef6555345dda667","tid":2081683,"uid":205043,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"郭窮城有冇得同mj一戰？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T12:30:49.000Z","msg":"小豬或者夠揪"},{"pid":"2d91